To-Do Web App with Flexbox
This project is a simple to-do web application styled using CSS Flexbox. The app allows users to organize their tasks for the week.

Features
Flexbox Layout: Utilizes CSS Flexbox for a responsive and dynamic layout.
Organized Tasks: Provides a structured layout for organizing tasks for each day of the week.
Reminders Section: Includes a reminders section for important notes or upcoming events.
How to Use
Clone the repository to your local machine.
Open the index.html file in your web browser.
Add or remove tasks as needed for each day of the week.
Utilize the reminders section for important notes or upcoming events.
Project Structure
index.html: Contains the HTML structure of the to-do web app.
style.css: Defines the styling and layout using CSS, including Flexbox properties.
README.md: Provides information about the project, its features, and how to use it.
